snippet.title: Loco Limbo first gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Hello, I'm Loco Limbo, waking up on an island after some crazy military experiments. 
Now, I can detach my own limbs and control 'em like puppets.Can I make it off this crazy island in one piece?
